rows.label: bf07260100_0020
rows.name: Fear not. He is going to be fine.

rows.label: bf07260100_0040
rows.name: The fact that you're alive is proof of that, is it not?

rows.label: bf07260100_0060
rows.name:
I had to transplant part of your Core Crystal
into his heart.

rows.label: bf07260100_0070
rows.name:
His wounds were grave.
It was the only way to save you both.
